<h2>Update animal details</h2>

<p>Besides health changes, our animals often turn out to be a different sex, species, sub-species or breed than we initially thought.</p>

<p>This page is for updating our animal records. Choose an animal from the drop-down menu and you'll be taken to their edit page.</p>

<form method="get" action = "/shelter/animals/updateselect">

  <select name="id">

    <label>

      <% for animal in @animals %>

        <option value="<%= animal.id %>">

            <%= animal.name %> the <%= animal.type %>

        </option>

      <% end %>

    </label>

  </select>

  <p>

    <input type="submit" value="Go to update animal details"/>

  </p>

</form>